		<text>Get Funds to Join Clear Sky</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_mar_smart_terrain_base_stalker_leader_marsh_cf_task_1_text">
		<text>Cold will indoctrinate you into Clear Sky for 15,000 RU.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_mar_smart_terrain_base_stalker_leader_marsh_cf_task_1_about">
		<text>Yes, we've been watching you. You will be a good fit for Clear Sky. We insist every initiate pays a 15,000 RU fee, this helps fund our research and pays our protection. What do you say?</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_mar_smart_terrain_base_stalker_leader_marsh_cf_task_1_finish">
		<text>Good. We're glad to have you aboard Clear Sky.</text>
	</string>

